-  Declaration order
        Related property declarations should be grouped together following the order:

        Positioning
              /* Positioning */
              position: absolute;
              top: 0;
              right: 0;
              bottom: 0;
              left: 0;
              z-index: 100;
        Box model
              /* Box-model */
              display: block;
              float: right;
              width: 100px;
              height: 100px;
        Typographic
        Visual
        Misc
    

